        "timestamp": 1740249736
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Looks like it is pub on mainline <a href=\"https://github.com/torvalds/linux/blob/ff202c5028a195c07b16e1a2fbb8ca6b7ba11a1c/rust/kernel/lib.rs#L42\">https://github.com/torvalds/linux/blob/ff202c5028a195c07b16e1a2fbb8ca6b7ba11a1c/rust/kernel/lib.rs#L42</a> but maybe not with your changes?</p>",
        "id": 501291382,
